## 📌 Project Outcome

Developed an **end-to-end interactive Power BI dashboard** that transforms raw mobile sales data into actionable business insights. The dashboard helps stakeholders monitor sales performance, customer behavior, and market trends through intuitive visualizations and dynamic filtering.

